verbose_text: The intense green fluorescence was detected in DF-1 cells transfected with pcDNA3.1 (+)-EtMIC2 and none was in those transfected with pcDNA3.1 (+) (XREF_FIG), demonstrating that the pcDNA3.1 (+)-EtMIC2 protein could be successfully expressed in vitro.
evidence: pcDNA3.1(+)-EtMIC2 protein could be successfully expressed
